{"ts": "2026-06-09T17:16:16.525027+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:gGyLME | successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 9a82d9f4334217060a4dffe829600ce34d6c91d0)", "id": "lc_98b30a7c-516f-45b1-bc14-f0febd426e7e"}, {"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:gGyLME | #!/usr/bin/env bash\n| MCP:gGyLME | \n| MCP:gGyLME | set -o errexit\n| MCP:gGyLME | set -o pipefail\n| MCP:gGyLME | set -o nounset\n| MCP:gGyLME | \n| MCP:gGyLME | # Rename tmdb_config.dart.sample file so that the project compiles\n| MCP:gGyLME | (cd core/lib/src && mv tmdb_config.dart.sample tmdb_config.dart)\n| MCP:gGyLME | \n| MCP:gGyLME | # Get all packages for core, mobile and web\n| MCP:gGyLME | (cd core && pub get)\n| MCP:gGyLME | (cd web && pub get)\n| MCP:gGyLME | (cd mobile && flutter packages get)\n| MCP:gGyLME | \n| MCP:gGyLME | # Analyze core, mobile and web\n| MCP:gGyLME | (cd core && dartanalyzer ./ --fatal-infos --fatal-warnings)\n| MCP:gGyLME | (cd mobile && dartanalyzer ./ --fatal-infos --fatal-warnings)\n| MCP:gGyLME | (cd web && dartanalyzer ./ --fatal-infos --fatal-warnings)\n| MCP:gGyLME | \n| MCP:gGyLME | # Run tests for core, mobile and web\n| MCP:gGyLME | echo \"--- Running tests in core... ---\"\n| MCP:gGyLME | (cd core && pub run test)\n| MCP:gGyLME | \n| MCP:gGyLME | echo \"--- Running tests in mobile... ---\"\n| MCP:gGyLME | (cd mobile && flutter test)\n| MCP:gGyLME | \n| MCP:gGyLME | echo \"--- Running tests in web... ---\"\n| MCP:gGyLME | (cd web && pub run build_runner test --fail-on-severe -- -p chrome)", "id": "lc_6f9943b2-578a-4dc8-9e33-0ae048bf8889"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "fb1cee7f-29fb-41a6-a6f9-29670bf97007", "tool_call_id": "call_5b3ba46073324083a26651a5", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
